### Provider API Tests
### Tests for ProviderController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### List all available providers
### Returns list of all configured AI providers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/providers
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get specific provider by name
### Returns details for a specific AI provider
# @prompt provider Replace with actual provider name (e.g., "zai", "openai")
GET http://localhost:8080/api/providers/{{provider}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Start OAuth authorization for provider
### Initiates OAuth flow for provider authentication
# @prompt provider Replace with actual provider name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/providers/{{provider}}/oauth/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "redirect_uri": "http://localhost:8080/callback"
}

###

### Handle OAuth callback for provider
### Completes OAuth flow with authorization code
# @prompt provider Replace with actual provider name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/providers/{{provider}}/oauth/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "authorization_code_from_provider",
  "state": "state_parameter"
}

###
